settings.description: A nuclear reactor powering Smaghetti’s servers. It’s being shut down for bogus reasons such as, “hazardous wastes”, and, “dangerous for the earth”. No Co2, just waste that can be buried really deep.
An ugly, gold temple from ancient times.
A level in which Toad has broken his leg, and can’t weed his lawn, and the Mario Bros. have been hired to help demolish a building due to past experience.
Bowser has taken control of the plains! Defeat his army and claim the plains!
